Package permafrost.tundra.server.content

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ChainedFilterContentHandler
    A content handler which wraps a list of chained content handlers where each handler is invoked in sequence to process content.
    ChainedFilterContentHandlerFactory
    A content handler factory which wraps a list of chained content handler factories where each factory is used in sequence to create a chained content handler.
    ContentHandlerInput
    Wraps the arguments to the ContentHandler getInputValues method, so that they can be mutated.
    ContentHandlerOutput
    Wraps the arguments to the ContentHandler putOutputValues method, so that they can be mutated.
    ContentManagerHelper
    A collection of convenience methods for working with the Integration Server ContentManager.
    FilterContentHandler
    An abstract class for a content handler which filters the inputs to another content handler.
    FilterContentHandlerFactory  
    HTTPCompressionContentHandler
    A custom content handler which implements support for HTTP compression using the gzip algorithm by wrapping another content handler, then checking if the request is HTTP and includes the `Content-Encoding: gzip` header and if so first wraps the input stream with a gzip decompresssion stream before calling the proxied content handler to process the request as normal.
    HTTPCompressionContentHandlerFactory
    An Integration Server content handler factory for HTTPCompressionContentHandler objects.
    HTTPStateHelper
    A collection of convenience methods for working with the Integration Server HTTPState object.
    JSONContentHandler
    An Integration Server content handler for JSON.
    JSONContentHandlerFactory
    An Integration Server content handler factory for JSON.
    LoggingContentHandler
    A content handler which logs all processed input content.
    LoggingContentHandlerFactory
    A factory for creating LoggingContentHandler objects.
    ProxyContentHandler
    An Integration Server content handler that proxies method calls to another content handler.
    ProxyContentHandlerFactory
    An Integration Server content handler factory that proxies method calls to another content handler factory.
